gate.lib.interaction.process

Class ProcessBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • gate.lib.interaction.process.ProcessBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Process4JsonStream, Process4ObjectStream, Process4StringStream, ProcessSimple

    public abstract class ProcessBase
extends Object
    Minimalist base class for exchanging objects with a command line process. The various subclasses of this implement more specific ways of how the data actually gets exchanged with the process.

      • updateCommand4OS

        protected void updateCommand4OS(List<String> command)
        Does an in-place update of the command to conform to what the OS expects. This is mainly about dealing with commands and arguments that contain spaces for now. On a Windows-like system, everything that contains spaces is surrounded with double quotes. On a Linux-like system, spaces are escaped with a backslash.
        Parameters:
        command - command
